尽管一开始的研究热点集中在解决[[P/NP问题|P/NP问题]]，但人们旋即意识到此类问题并不是DNA运算的最佳应用场合，以致有多种意见要求寻找[[杀手级应用|杀手级应用]]。1997年，计算机学家 [[Mitsunori_Ogihara|Mitsunori Ogihara]]和生物学家Animesh Ray一道提出了一种[[组合逻辑电路|组合逻辑电路]]的评价方法，并描绘了实现方法。<ref>M. Ogihara and A. Ray, [http://wwwcp.tphys.uni-heidelberg.de/comp-phys/handouts/Boolean2.pdf "Simulating Boolean circuits on a DNA computer"] {{Wayback|url=http://wwwcp.tphys.uni-heidelberg.de/comp-phys/handouts/Boolean2.pdf |date=20120425064657 }}.
Algorithmica 25:239–250, 1999.</ref><ref>[http://partners.nytimes.com/library/cyber/week/052197dna.html "In Just a Few Drops, A Breakthrough in Computing"] {{Wayback|url=http://partners.nytimes.com/library/cyber/week/052197dna.html |date=20120402134439 }}, ''[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]'', May 21, 1997</ref>
2002年，来自[[Weizmann_Institute_of_Science|Weizmann Institute of Science]]的研究者公开了一种由DNA分子和酶，而不是硅组成的计算机器。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2003/02/0224_030224_DNAcomputer.html |title=Computer Made from DNA and Enzymes |accessdate=2009-11-26 |last=Lovgren |first=Stefan |date=2003-02-24 |work=National Geographic |archive-date=2003-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030226202101/http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2003/02/0224_030224_DNAcomputer.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2004年3月28日，[[Weizmann_Institute|Weizmann Institute]]的[[Ehud_Shapiro|Ehud Shapiro]], Yaakov Benenson, Binyamin Gil, Uri Ben-Dor,和Rivka Adar在[[自然_(期刊)|自然]]杂志上发表文章称，他们实现了一种整合了输入输出的DNA计算机，理论上可以实现细胞内的[[癌症|癌症]]诊断，并释放抗癌药物。DNA分子由四种碱基组成，通过酶改变他们的排列可以进行计算。<ref>{{cite journal|title=DNA-based computing of strategic assignment problems|journal=Physical Review Letters|date=3 May 2011|first1=Jian-Jun|last1=Shu|first2=Q.-W.|last2=Wang|first3=K.-Y.|last3=Yong|volume=106|issue=18|pages=188702|doi=10.1103/PhysRevLett.106.188702|pmid=21635133|s2cid=25989989|bibcode=2011PhRvL.106r8702S}}</ref><ref name=“ShuDNAGPS”>{{cite journal|title=Programmable DNA-mediated multitasking processor|journal=Journal of Physical Chemistry B|date=30 April 2015|first1=Jian-Jun|last1=Shu|first2=Q.-W.|last2=Wang|first3=K.-Y.|last3=Yong|first4=F.|last4=Shao|first5=K.J.|last5=Lee|volume=119|issue=17|pages=5639–5644|doi=10.1021/acs.jpcb.5b02165|pmid=25874653|s2cid=10446710|arxiv=1508.03509|bibcode=2015arXiv150803509S}}</ref> 近日，英国科学家成功的在一小团DNA中存储了大量文件，并成功读取。<ref name="shapiro_cancer">{{cite journal|url=http://www.nature.com/articles/nature02551|pages=423–429|title=An autonomous molecular computer for logical control of gene expression|journal=Nature|volume=429|issue=6990|issn=1476-4687|date=2004/05|language=En|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1038/nature02551|author=Yaakov Benenson, Binyamin Gil, Uri Ben-Dor, Rivka Adar, Ehud Shapiro|archive-date=2019-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215214948/https://www.nature.com/articles/nature02551|dead-url=no}}. Also aviable here: {{cite web |url=http://www.wisdom.weizmann.ac.il/~udi/papers/automoleculcomp_nat04.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-10-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402153014/http://www.wisdom.weizmann.ac.il/~udi/papers/automoleculcomp_nat04.pdf |archivedate=2012-04-02 }}</ref>

